ACKNOWLEDGMENTS:

This project builds upon and credits the following work:

1. HMJS Library by Tom Quist
   - Repository: https://github.com/tomquist/hmjs
   - License: MIT License
   - Contribution: Original HM device protocol implementation and BLE communication patterns

2. Marstek Venus E Firmware Research
   - Repository: https://github.com/rweijnen/marstek-venus-e-firmware-notes
   - Contribution: Protocol analysis, firmware reverse engineering, and command structure documentation

The Marstek Venus E Monitor is an independent project that extends the HM protocol 
to work with Marstek Venus E battery systems, following the same architectural 
patterns and communication methods pioneered by the original HMJS project.

